---
---

<section class="section pricing" id="precios">
  <div class="container pricing-inner">
    <div class="pricing-text">
      <h2 class="section-title">¿Cuánto cuesta tu proyecto?</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Descarga nuestra lista de precios y conoce las tarifas por material y
        tiempo de máquina.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-action">
      <a
        href="/precios-lumoarte.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn btn-primary pricing-btn"
      >
        <svg
          width="18"
          height="18"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path>
          <polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline>
          <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
        </svg>
        Descargar lista de precios (PDF)
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-surface);
  }

  .pricing-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .pricing-text .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .pricing-btn {
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .pricing-btn {
      white-space: normal;
    }
  }
</style>
